# ── Generated image derivatives ────────────────────────────────────────────
# src/assets/products/ is produced from Images/ by `npm run images`. Committing
# it would store all 146 photographs a second time (~108 MB) for no benefit.
# Clone, run `npm run images`, then build.
site/src/assets/products/

